abstract:
We obtain local boundedness of weak solutions of double phase quasilinear parabolic equations of the form \[u_t-	ext{div} \left(|
abla u|^{p-2}
abla u+a(x,t)|
abla u|^{q-2}
abla uight)=0,\] where, we have imposed the restrictions $ rac{2N}{N+2}<p<\infty$, $0\leq a(x,t)\leq M$ is measurable and $q < p rac{N+1}{N-1}$.
